## Conclusion
Duration: 1

At the end of your Sigma Quickstart, always have a clear call to action (CTA). This CTA could be a link to the docs pages, links to videos on youtube, a GitHub repo link, etc. 

If you want to learn more about Sigma Quickstart formatting, checkout the official documentation here: [Formatting Guide](https://github.com/googlecodelabs/tools/blob/master/FORMAT-GUIDE.md)

